information, a broader

00:03:21.530 --> 00:03:25.000
community around it, and you
probably all have used

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:26.840
Fandango for showtimes.

00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:29.560
We like to believe that
moviegoing is

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:32.220
largely a social event.

00:03:32.220 --> 00:03:34.220
Maybe every now and then
you go by yourself.

00:03:34.220 --> 00:03:37.390
