around moviegoing where

00:03:40.560 --> 00:03:45.680
you're in three distinct
phases.

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:48.150
Discovery and consideration,
where you're watching

00:03:48.150 --> 00:03:51.580
trailers, maybe checking out
reviews, looking at photos,

00:03:51.580 --> 00:03:53.250
just learning about movies.

00:03:53.250 --> 00:03:55.640
