you're actually going, you're

00:03:55.640 --> 00:03:58.430
in a planning and buying mode.

00:03:58.430 --> 00:04:01.570
And then afterwards, you're
in a discussion mode.

00:04:01.570 --> 00:04:05.550
And all these phases have
social touchpoints where

00:04:05.550 --> 00:04:08.040
you're communicating with either
your immediate friends

00:04:08.040 --> 00:04:10.620
or a larger moviegoing
community at large.

00:04:10.620 --> 00:04:13.580
So one of the things that
we've focused on in our

00:04:13.580 --> 00:04:17.490
implementation that we're
showing here is the middle

00:04:17.490 --> 00:04:18.640
phase, where--

00:04:18.640 --> 00:04:21.649
that's kind of our sweet spot
of planning and going.

00:04:21.649 --> 00:04:24.800
