sign-in page here to make it

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:28.210
really easy, have multiple
options for sign-in.

00:04:28.210 --> 00:04:31.250
If you want to carry your
identity with you from Google

00:04:31.250 --> 00:04:33.610
or if you already have a
Fandango login, we can tie the

00:04:33.610 --> 00:04:35.160
two together.

00:04:35.160 --> 00:04:36.910
If you go to the next slide.

00:04:36.910 --> 00:04:40.210
You can see, this is a typical
showtimes page.

00:04:40.210 --> 00:04:45.430
