00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:05.120
So you don't need to
be on Fandango.

00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:06.620
You don't need to
send an email.

00:05:06.620 --> 00:05:09.260
You're alerting them across
multiple platforms.

00:05:09.260 --> 00:05:12.845
So we think that's going to
have great reach for our

00:05:12.845 --> 00:05:16.330
community and be able to join
people in a way they haven't

00:05:16.330 --> 00:05:19.720
really done before.

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:21.240
That's one instance of it.

00:05:21.240 --> 00:05:23.690
We plan to roll out across
all the multiple

00:05:23.690 --> 00:05:26.330
touchpoints pre and post.

00:05:26.330 --> 00:05:28.560
So this was a great
start to it.

00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:30.180
It's an interactive post.

00:05:30.180 --> 00:05:33.360
And I think that another flavor
that we're talking

00:05:33.360 --> 00:05:36.540
